  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A wizard from the School of Transmutation can create this object with 8 hours of work. A creature with this object gains one of the following benefits, as decided by the stone's creator:</p><ul><li><strong>Darkvision</strong> out to a range of 60 feet</li><li>An increase to speed of 10 feet while the creature is <strong>unencumbered</strong></li><li>Proficiency in Constitution saving throws</li><li><strong>Resistance</strong> to acid, cold, fire, lightning, or thunder damage (your choice whenever you choose this benefit)</li></ul><p>If you are the creator of this object, each time you cast a <strong>transmutation</strong> spell of 1st level or higher, you can change the effect of your stone if the stone is on your person.</p><section id=\"secret-sUB25oZtymVSI58i\" class=\"secret\"><p><em>Note: This item has a passive effect for each trait. Toggle the desired one on. The damage resistance effect will need to be updated to the desired damage type.</em></p><p><em>This item must be equipped for effects to take apply.</em></p></section>",
